original: Branzell, Oscar Walter, fabrikör, Brämhult, f. 30/8/03 i Borås av brand-niäst. Carl B. o. Cecilia Gabrielsson. G. 32 m. Anna-Lisa Marcusson. Barn: Ulla-Britta f. 33, Gudrun 36, Kerstin 39. — Avg:ex. fr. Borås tekn. vävsk. 20. Anst. v. Kristinedals Nya Ullspinn. i Lidköp. 22-26, i A-B Ludvig Andersson i Kinna 26-35, inneh. av Borås Mattväveri fr. 35, Branzell & Persson A-B fr. 45. Styr :led. i A-B Borås Mattväveri 45.
translated: Branzell, Oscar Walter, manufacturer, Brämhult, b. 30/8/03 in Borås to Carl B. and Cecilia Gabrielsson, who were firefighters. Married in 1932 to Anna-Lisa Marcusson. Children: Ulla-Britta b. 1933, Gudrun b. 1936, Kerstin b. 1939. Graduated from Borås Technical Weaving School in 1920. Employed at Kristinedals Nya Ullspinn in Lidköping from 1922-1926, and A-B Ludvig Andersson in Kinna from 1926-1935. Owner of Borås Mattväveri from 1935, and Branzell & Persson A-B from 1945. Board member of A-B Borås Mattväveri starting in 1945.
